### Books - Search and Filter Operations
### Environment variables from ../environments.env

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv baseUrl}}
@apiUrl = {{$dotenv apiUrl}}

###
### Search Books by Title
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=java
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search Books by Author
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=martin
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search Books by Keywords
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=programming
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search with Pagination
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=architecture&page=1&limit=3
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Advanced Search with Multiple Filters
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=java&author=Joshua&minRating=4.0&maxPages=500
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search by Publisher
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?publisher=Addison-Wesley
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search by Publication Year Range
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?publishedAfter=2015-01-01&publishedBefore=2020-01-01
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search by Language
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?language=en
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search by Tags
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?tags=Programming,Java
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search with Sorting
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=programming&sortBy=rating&sortOrder=desc
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search Available Books Only
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=clean&availableOnly=true
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Full Text Search
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=agile software craftsmanship&searchType=fulltext
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Empty Search Query (should return all books)
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search with No Results
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=nonexistentbook12345
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Search with Special Characters
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?q=C++
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Invalid Search Parameters (Error Test)
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/search?page=-1&limit=1000
Content-Type: application/json